### GET /node/user

This endpoint retrieves user information.

#### Request

No request body is required for this endpoint.

#### Response

The response will be in JSON format with the following schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "code": {
      "type": "number"
    },
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "id": {
          "type": "number"
        },
        "name": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "email": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "type": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "avatar": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "semester": {
          "type": "number"
        },
        "semester_name": {
          "type": ["string", "null"]
        },
        "department_id": {
          "type": "number"
        },
        "department_name": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "group": {
          "type": "number"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```
